la mayor responsabilidad.

00:56:22.869 --> 00:56:23.939
Sal de aquí.

00:56:52.300 --> 00:56:55.410
(Vicepresidente Kang Tae Min)

00:57:11.090 --> 00:57:12.490
Sí, Soo Kyung.

00:57:14.689 --> 00:57:16.729
